                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-1104" type="given" value="FREDERICK WILLIAM"></interp>FREDERICK WILLIAM TAYLOB</persName>
                  </hi>. I saw some stockings in Mr. Poeoek's kitchen, one was lying on the chair in which Richardson was sitting—they did not belong to the house—they had been brought there.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Johnson's Defence</hi>. I picked up the handkerchief.</p>
